in<i>“METAL SLUG 3”</i> at any time,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and compete with other players to become the world's No. 1 soldier!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>** WILL NOT RUN ON XP **</strong></p>",
